OL,5,G0140 Kate Bush: The Timeless Genius
OL,6,     FHow has the woman nicknamed the
OL,7,     F'Sound Witch' managed to transcend
OL,8,     Feras and trends, remaining as
OL,9,     Fmodern and fascinating as ever?
OL,10,     FWhat accounts for her timeless
OL,11,     Fgenius? Documentary.
OL,12,G0250 Wuthering Heights: Love, Hate and
OL,13,G     Vengeance
OL,14,     FNarrating the doomed romance of
OL,15,     FHeathcliff and Catherine, the
OL,16,     Fstory contains a powerful critique
OL,17,     Fof British society, denouncing its
OL,18,     Foppressive system.
